  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/b178c0745155b32e13edc0326410a54b.avif?t=1738711557\" width=618 height=104 /></span>You will have to help the brave legendary beaver, who fearlessly overcomes all obstacles. Exciting adventures and clashes with various opponents are waiting for you.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/5b214f577afab460a374edb53a4666cb.poster.avif?t=1738711557\" width=291 height=73 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/5b214f577afab460a374edb53a4666cb.webm?t=1738711557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOBR SPRINT This is an old-school platformer, with increasing levels of difficulty. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increasing difficulty is done by increasing the number of obstacles and enemies on the level, the appearance of dynamic platforms, obstacles and traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/42c79693dcd1515e563e6f8650caf452.poster.avif?t=1738711557\" width=381 height=79 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/42c79693dcd1515e563e6f8650caf452.webm?t=1738711557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/ec445dc8ba451d6ddd12a70d8d202c7f.poster.avif?t=1738711557\" width=225 height=55 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/ec445dc8ba451d6ddd12a70d8d202c7f.webm?t=1738711557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight enemies, find secrets, run through levels that have an obstacle system lined up</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Old-school platformer is a game that incorporates elements of classic games from the 1980s and 1990s. This genre is characterized by simple character control, linear levels with hidden secrets and bosses, and classic pixel-art graphics. A feature of this genre is the high level of difficulty, requiring the player to react quickly and be precise in controlling the character.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/b178c0745155b32e13edc0326410a54b.avif?t=1738711557\" width=618 height=104 /></span>You will have to help the brave legendary beaver, who fearlessly overcomes all obstacles. Exciting adventures and clashes with various opponents are waiting for you.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/5b214f577afab460a374edb53a4666cb.poster.avif?t=1738711557\" width=291 height=73 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/5b214f577afab460a374edb53a4666cb.webm?t=1738711557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BOBR SPRINT This is an old-school platformer, with increasing levels of difficulty. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increasing difficulty is done by increasing the number of obstacles and enemies on the level, the appearance of dynamic platforms, obstacles and traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/42c79693dcd1515e563e6f8650caf452.poster.avif?t=1738711557\" width=381 height=79 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/42c79693dcd1515e563e6f8650caf452.webm?t=1738711557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/ec445dc8ba451d6ddd12a70d8d202c7f.poster.avif?t=1738711557\" width=225 height=55 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467000/extras/ec445dc8ba451d6ddd12a70d8d202c7f.webm?t=1738711557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight enemies, find secrets, run through levels that have an obstacle system lined up</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Old-school platformer is a game that incorporates elements of classic games from the 1980s and 1990s. This genre is characterized by simple character control, linear levels with hidden secrets and bosses, and classic pixel-art graphics. A feature of this genre is the high level of difficulty, requiring the player to react quickly and be precise in controlling the character.</p></li></ul>",
